    <properties>
        <title>Mod4j 1.2.0 Release Notes</title>
    </properties>
    <body>
        <section name="Mod4j 1.2.0 Release Notes">

            <p>
                Dear Mod4j community,
                <br />
                <br />
                The Mod4j development team is pleased to announce the release of Mod4j 1.2.0.
                Below
                you can find the complete list of solved bugs, improvements and new features for
                this release.
            </p>

            <subsection name="How to upgrade">
                <p>
                    If you want to upgrade from the previous Mod4j release, you will need to follow
                    the required upgrade steps
                    as described in the
                    <a href="upgradenotes.html">Mod4j 1.2.0 Upgrade Notes</a>
                </p>
            </subsection>
            <subsection name="Mod4j 1.2.0 Relaese Notes List">
                <h2> Bug</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        [
                        <a href='http://jira.codehaus.org/browse/MODFORJ-97'>MODFORJ-97</a>
                        ] - A site deploy does not copy site pages for the first time
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        [
                        <a href='http://jira.codehaus.org/browse/MODFORJ-147'>MODFORJ-147</a>
                        ] - Mod4j appears to need plugin org.apache.commons.cli
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        [
                        <a href='http://jira.codehaus.org/browse/MODFORJ-150'>MODFORJ-150</a>
                        ] - DtoTranslators perform the fromDto incorerct in certain cases
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        [
                        <a href='http://jira.codehaus.org/browse/MODFORJ-151'>MODFORJ-151</a>
                        ] - toBeRemoved variable generated mutiple times
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        [
                        <a href='http://jira.codehaus.org/browse/MODFORJ-152'>MODFORJ-152</a>
                        ] - The Mod4j unittests should be timezone independent
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        [
                        <a href='http://jira.codehaus.org/browse/MODFORJ-170'>MODFORJ-170</a>]
                        - Hibernate mapping is missing the mandatory(?) &quot;key&quot; element
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <h2> Improvement</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        [
                        <a href='http://jira.codehaus.org/browse/MODFORJ-140'>MODFORJ-140</a>
                        ] - Remove setId() method in dto's
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        [
                        <a href='http://jira.codehaus.org/browse/MODFORJ-153'>MODFORJ-153</a>
                        ] - Dto-translators depend on service model
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        [
                        <a href='http://jira.codehaus.org/browse/MODFORJ-169'>MODFORJ-169</a>
                        ] - Remove ListDto, they are not needed
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <h2> New Feature</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        [
                        <a href='http://jira.codehaus.org/browse/MODFORJ-155'>MODFORJ-155</a>
                        ] - Implement service methods for paging support
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        [
                        <a href='http://jira.codehaus.org/browse/MODFORJ-164'>MODFORJ-164</a>
                        ] - Add sorting parameter to the listAll service methods
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </subsection>
        </section>
    </body>
</document>
